        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-09-21 13:24:20.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nBuild failure has nothing to do with this code. \nThe problem is in LocalLur and its tests, where for local RBAC User is renewing permExpiration with the code:\n\npublic void renewPerm() {\n        permExpires = System.currentTimeMillis()+interval;\n    }\nwhile interval is 0L there, there is a chance that validation passes in the test, only when the code is run in the same millisecond.\nTesting hazard...\n@IanHowell is the owner of failing test from 15.05.2018",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
